directory:  /home/mayukh/utils/espresso-5.0.2/bin/
examples directory: /home/mayukh/utils/espresso-5.0.2/examples/
To run a single processor job:
  Goto: /home/mayukh/utils/espresso-5.0.2/examples/examples/example01/results
  Type: pw.x < al.scf.david.in > myout
To run a multi processor job:
  Goto: /home/mayukh/utils/espresso-5.0.2/examples/examples/example01/results
  Type for 8 processors:  
    /home/mayukh/utils/mpich2-install/bin/mpirun -np 8 pw.x < al.scf.david.in  > myout
    /home/mayukh/utils/mpich2-install/bin/mpirun -np 8 /home/mayukh/utils/espresso-5.0.2/bin/pw.x < al.scf.david.in  > myout


